### Document Structure

- Minimize DOM depth — deep nesting increases layout recalculation time
- Avoid excessive DOM nodes — browser struggles above ~1500 nodes
- Put critical CSS inline in `<head>`, load non-critical CSS asynchronously
  ```html
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="non-critical.css" media="print" onload="this.media='all'" />
  ```
- Use semantic HTML — `<header>`, `<main>`, `<article>` parse faster and improve accessibility

