### 12. API Response Time Targets

| Response time | Assessment |
|---|---|
| < 100ms | Excellent — perceived as instant |
| 100–300ms | Good |
| 300–1000ms | Acceptable — consider caching or optimization |
| 1–3s | Poor — user notices the wait |
| > 3s | Unacceptable — must fix |

> **Target p95 < 300ms** for most endpoints. **p99 < 1s.** Never optimize for average latency alone.

